{"tid":2069166,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"BLM殺到game界,PS5《 Little Devil Inside 》開發商公開致歉","createTime":"2020-06-18T07:50:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-25T11:21:53.000Z","uid":103207,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"eb655b890cf0ca7163792309449db1c461488fb4","tid":2069166,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T07:50:02.000Z","msg":"《 Little Devil Inside 》開發商公開致歉 PS5新作涉及種族歧視<br />\n<br />\n游雲&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家還記得在6月11日舉辦的PS5線上遊戲發佈會嗎？於這次的發佈中展示了很多PS5的新作，但令人想不到的是，當中有一款名為《 Little Devil Inside 》的作品，由於創作的角色涉及到種族歧視而受到玩家的抨擊。<br />\n<br />\n《 Little Devil Inside 》宣傳影片<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_FqsyNSYSKc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_FqsyNSYSKc&d=j4yDeGq49jMu68ZzGhcJHjw60zqfRdeCYg0zJNkavsY%3D&h=91d65d9b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_FqsyNSYSKc</a><br />\n<br />\n於官方公佈的影片中看到，這款以冒險作主題的遊戲中，<span style=\"color: red;\">主角將會遇上一些戴著面具的土人，而這些土人更是厚嘴唇、黑皮膚，以及紮辮子，不少玩家都反映這種方式是對黑人的刻板印象，這種角色設計是完全沒有必要。</span><br />\n<br />\n《 Little Devil Inside 》涉及種類歧視的角色<br />\n<br />\n此消息一出，旋即受到廣大玩家的留意，<span style=\"color: red;\">而開發商 Neostream 亦立即出面澄清，指本身在創作時不打算使用任何具種族主義的方向，亦絕不會有任何加入真實的非洲或美國黑人的想法，而工作室方面將糾正相關的錯誤，去除辮子，改變嘴唇外觀及膚色，如果感覺仍有不足的話，將會再次重新設計相關角色。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://greatgame.asia/%e3%80%8a-little-devil-inside-%e3%80%8b%e9%96%8b%e7%99%bc%e5%95%86%e5%85%ac%e9%96%8b%e8%87%b4%e6%ad%89-ps5%e6%96%b0%e4%bd%9c%e6%b6%89%e5%8f%8a%e7%a8%ae%e6%97%8f%e6%ad%a7%e8%a6%96/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgreatgame.asia%2F%25e3%2580%258a-little-devil-inside-%25e3%2580%258b%25e9%2596%258b%25e7%2599%25bc%25e5%2595%2586%25e5%2585%25ac%25e9%2596%258b%25e8%2587%25b4%25e6%25ad%2589-ps5%25e6%2596%25b0%25e4%25bd%259c%25e6%25b6%2589%25e5%258f%258a%25e7%25a8%25ae%25e6%2597%258f%25e6%25ad%25a7%25e8%25a6%2596%2F&d=j4yDeGq49jMu68ZzGhcJHjw60zqfRdeCYg0zJNkavsY%3D&h=151e4dd0\" target=\"_blank\">https://greatgame.asia/%e3%80%8a-little-devil-inside-%e3%80%8b%e9%96%8b%e7%99%bc%e5%95%86%e5%85%ac%e9%96%8b%e8%87%b4%e6%ad%89-ps5%e6%96%b0%e4%bd%9c%e6%b6%89%e5%8f%8a%e7%a8%ae%e6%97%8f%e6%ad%a7%e8%a6%96/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;"},{"pid":"200fd11abfa52fb834abc60c2f44e3fe47dd605a","tid":2069166,"uid":123264,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T07:52:08.000Z","msg":"估計唔會變白人 會變黃種人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為對黃種人racist係無人理 黑鳩就大哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea93577f7bb23d35be33ad474102f2e9605965d9","tid":2069166,"uid":7609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T07:56:50.000Z","msg":"幾時將d左膠黑人漂白<br />\n左膠白人變黑人？"},{"pid":"2cb81656351363daef95e17abbe1113651d5a6a7","tid":2069166,"uid":103207,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T07:58:28.000Z","msg":"隻GAME得白人,冇黑人= Racist<br />\n<br />\n隻GAME有黑人,但唔啱佢地心水= Racist<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07ee555544ff3158b42243b8fddd0a15fa3256f8","tid":2069166,"uid":159183,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T08:50:14.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<br />\n發佈會最期待呢隻<br />\nd左膠未搞咁多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a15d973d7f1a28870edb3dfadfc77b430240b0d6","tid":2069166,"uid":34409,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T16:28:44.000Z","msg":"當年紅唇娃都係咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sN74Cxt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsN74Cxt.jpg&h=6a351a4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t3mXXxw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft3mXXxw.jpg&h=2f636718&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d8bc4cb2be2ea93edc91d647bf7f8bd2d3a56cf8","tid":2069166,"uid":6424,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2cb816563